    <h1 style="color:#d8ac29;text-align:center;padding-top:20px;">THE SECRUIT</h1>
    <p style="color:#d8ac29;">This is a Web-Integrated Machine Learning Module which primarily has three sections :<h3 style="color:#d8ac29;">JobAssist</h3>Our Job Assistance System which can help Enginnering Students to get a brief idea of which Job Role they are likely to acquire.This could also help Corporate Farms to get an idea of which role they should give to a particular indiviual on the basis of their Academic as well as professonal details.<br><h3 style="color:#d8ac29;">Analysis</h3>In this section we have done a overall analysis of our dataset used which could help the user of getting an overview of various job-traits.<br><h3 style="color:#d8ac29;">My Profile</h3> This is where the user will be able to assess their traits in particular fields and can also keep an track of academic progrees required to get their Dream Job </p>
